  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Molamola Adventure\"</strong> is a danmaku shooting game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will control a molamola and embark on an underwater adventure alongside a  girl.<br>dodging bullets and defeating dangerous sea creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Type:</strong> danmaku shooting game.<br><strong>Game Duration:</strong> Approximately 30 minutes to 2 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arrow keys:</strong> Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Z key:</strong> Shoot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>X key:</strong> Bomb (available from Stage 2)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shift:</strong> Slow movement<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144240/extras/1dcf2461e1a8f87b61e365611cb2382f.avif?t=1736504133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144240/extras_big/1dcf2461e1a8f87b61e365611cb2382f.avif?t=1736504133 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bomb can clear enemy bullets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144240/extras/af19ca97493ded55d6ab22226a72b8c7.avif?t=1736504133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144240/extras_big/af19ca97493ded55d6ab22226a72b8c7.avif?t=1736504133 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
